<a href="/eq/board?board.id=Trade">Artisans Way (Tradeskill Discussion)</a> - <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=Trade&message.id=9892">Success Breakpoints for Producing GM Armor</a><p>


		<table cellpadding=4 cellspacing=0 border=1 width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td><td>Success Breakpoints for Producing GM Armor</td></tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="msg_user_cell" width="200" valign=top>
				
					<span style='color:#CC6600;font-weight:bold; '>LeanaSoulwarden</span>
